CROCK POT

2 pckg (3 oz each) ramen noodle soup mix (should include noodles)
1.25 lbs boneless, skinless chicken thighs,
	cut into 1-inch pieces
2 cups baby-cut carrots
1 medium red bell pepper, coarsely choppes (about 1 cup)
1 teaspoon finely chopped gingerroot
	(or 1/2 teaspoon ground ginger)
1.5 cups water
2 tblspoons teriyaki baste and glaze
8 oz peas (about 2 cups)

Mix soup mix, chicken, carrots, bell pepper, ginger, water, and teriyaki glaze
in 3 to 4 quart cooker

Cover and cook on low 7-9 hours

Add peas to cooker.
Break up noodles and add to cooker.
Increase setting to high. Cover and cook 15-20 minutes.
